
1) Allowing the same interface for KLsetTraceLevel and KLtrace: 
   e.g. use always a string instead of a number and a string
	 
2) introduce a customization of KLtrace behaviour, and debugging
   environment setup with KLsetTraceOption
	 
	 KLsetTraceOptions(UWORD32 flags)
	
	 flags: bit 0 SHOW_FILENAME instruct KLtrace to display module filename
	        bit 1 SHOW_LINENUM  instruct KLtrace to display listing line number
					
3) introduce KLgetProfilingData which return the minimum quantum usable
   to profile SK/CK code, the relative error and such data in a HW 
	 indipendent way
	 
4) collate things with gdb
	 
	 Stefano
